\pard\qc\b\f1 Crop Yield Prediction Using Machine Learning and a Lightweight Web-Based Decision Support System\b0\par
\pard\qc Your Name\par
\pard\qc Department of Computer Science, Your Institution\par
\pard\qc City, Country\par
